nodes.text: FX9 was a medical droid in service to the Galactic Empire and Darth Vader shortly following the Battle of Hoth.
FX9 was placed on the Executor and was the medical droid in charge of the recuperation of the Imperial spy, Shira Brie as she recovered in a bacta tank.
FX9 was created by David Michelinie, Walter Simonson and Tom Palmer.
